                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-191-18770108 t18770108-191-punishment-27"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">BOWYER</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18770108-191-punishment-28" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18770108-191-punishment-28" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
